{"tid":346675,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[too long] 認真地鳩噏連登現象","createTime":"2017-08-04T06:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T22:03:43.000Z","uid":63452,"like":13,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b41f6c76917cb52fd2f9ebbb93f1f06467c0dc84","tid":346675,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:57:10.000Z","msg":"唔知開咩台好，求其揀創意台算<br />\n純粹想鳩噏下下對連登/連登會員 嘅睇法，有咩唔同意嘅一齊討論下又得，負皮上一頁又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一. 論釣新會<del>員</del>然</span><br />\n<br />\n釣新會員呢樣嘢其實可以話一向都有<br />\n方法都不外乎post 下潮文，唔知係潮文嘅咪會認真討論/回覆，知係潮文嘅就 &ldquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&rdquo;, &quot;又一個新會然&rdquo;， &quot;恥笑開始&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n成件事俾我嘅觀感就係 <span style=\"color: red;\">扮老屎忽拎優越感</span><br />\n先唔講有幾多真係舊登移民過黎嘅 真。老屎忽<br />\n一個公開俾任何人申請ac 嘅論壇，實會有新血加入，亦都會有舊人唔再上論壇<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新舊交替下，新會員唔識以前嘅gag/文化 根本好正常</span><br />\n你可以話班新會員唔識google 下先覆人，衝出黎柒 (以前申請舊登ac 前我都係做左幾年cd rom 先）<br />\n但係<span style=\"color: red;\">就算俾你成功釣到，我唔明點解班 真/偽 老屎忽咁都可以拃取到優越感 同埋 釣左咁多次都笑得出重樂此不疲</span><br />\n<br />\n大家都做過新會員，亦都可能俾人成功釣過<br />\n依家班新會員只係做緊以前嘅我地<br />\n但係<span style=\"color: red;\">呢種七十後笑八十後，八十後笑九十後，九十後笑00 後 嘅風氣 令到唔少post 變左鬥老大會，騎劫左成個討論</span><br />\n<br />\n加上，就當你都上足十幾年兩登，除非你係每日廿四小時都捕住個forum 嘅隱閉青年，如果唔係都<span style=\"color: red;\">無可能記得/知道 每個gag 或者潮文</span><br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\">釣新會員呢個行為真係好無Q 謂</span>"},{"pid":"426de584bf85b32434033d92e95d0144e78fa0f6","tid":346675,"uid":83754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:59:44.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"5c55cb87fb390fa13596ba274d1285c518a5a7a3","tid":346675,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>55</blockquote><br />\n啱呀"},{"pid":"d965cc16660d7c3aad5cf7a21bb7d30726c0eb15","tid":346675,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:10:09.000Z","msg":"成堆90後打曬飛機，否則佢地可以有乜搞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：50後"},{"pid":"e9d45f359522cc83c12164a6068fef406ed097ba","tid":346675,"uid":1139,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:11:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1386edb702a58d4d8e52aa1658dfea976febcff2","tid":346675,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:18:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>體諒下，廢青冇野做系甘</blockquote><br />\n召喚肥絲捉鳩你正字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2beefd1c5d0880972ad31718e21b9676179011e","tid":346675,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:31:40.000Z","msg":"同感"},{"pid":"fa875ca2160c9be7d875f8c77c34bfc0b611cfd8","tid":346675,"uid":46737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:33:37.000Z","msg":"打段野出黎屌舊會員, 想釣新會員正評?"},{"pid":"3b3bf9b5698919f4947dc3d7b0ca525373dbfa6f","tid":346675,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:37:37.000Z","msg":"總之個感覺就覺得啲人上網係想刷存在感搏出位<br />\n心態問題最大"},{"pid":"358bb450ffac8cce8c0299e105e6af94cfb25a1f","tid":346675,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:38:53.000Z","msg":"無問題都唔會上連登啦"},{"pid":"8a7be7dc0ab2577241be982559da54c1a2653c05","tid":346675,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打段野出黎屌舊會員, 想釣新會員正評?</blockquote><br />\n與其係到玩誅心論，不如指出我講嘅嘢有咩錯？<br />\n<br />\n不過你提出嘅釣正評風氣咁啱就係下一樣我想講嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1596f44b69107a3681cf86e407d4d21524332165","tid":346675,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無問題都唔會上連登啦</blockquote><br />\n駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a525b027beb3ed4abaca611bf81c620b3aaaf35","tid":346675,"uid":124689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T08:15:40.000Z","msg":"米就糸牙，班老屎忽刀5知做乜9"},{"pid":"3e8dec21fe43ece9f11d059c66c97ed7c1859ad6","tid":346675,"uid":63452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T08:21:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">二. 論釣正評</span><br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，就係<span style=\"color: red;\">嗰排吹咩風，連登仔就跟咩風</span><br />\n嗰排吹正字，個個就認字特警上身，接個&ldquo;吾你老母&rdquo; 龍可以接足幾版<br />\n呢排興屌柒肥絲，就成班撲出黎開post 話邊個quote 肥絲就見一個block 一個<br />\n有句&rdquo;幽默感係唔可以勉強&rdquo; 嘅comment 係原post 好多人正皮，自始係好多post 都見到人係唔係都引用返呢句黎嘗試笑人<br />\n前排嘅一句&ldquo;積口德&rdquo; 令成個連登突然吹起冷血風，左一句 &ldquo;口德村村民&rdquo; 右一句 &ldquo;口德分-10&quot;<br />\n見到任何慘劇同新聞，不分青紅皂白咁留句冷血嘅comment 就會一呼百應<br />\n只要女人係雞係公廁，個女仔夏天凌晨出街著sportswear 跑步差啲俾人老強 都可以俾人講成臭雞引人犯罪，害左個大好青年<br />\n<br />\n同類事情多不勝數<br />\n以上每件事都足以開一個新topic 講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過<span style=\"color: red;\">共同點就係反映出連登仔人講咩就講咩，見風轉舵，最緊要就係搏到人認同</span><br />\n<br />\n正評將受人認同嘅程度量化成數字<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\">唔少連登仔上連登嘅唯一目的就係盲目追求正評/認同<br />\n結果連登變成一個大型暖爐俾大家圍爐取暖</span>"},{"pid":"c4037d5333c6d417dcd23ba2005fb39d0ad93748","tid":346675,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T08:40:25.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2fdcbd459d51a4180ecbe60898d22cb0f2ab770e","tid":346675,"uid":59832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T08:57:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%BF%B4%E8%81%B2%E5%AE%A4%E6%95%88%E6%87%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25BF%25B4%25E8%2581%25B2%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E6%2595%2588%25E6%2587%2589&d=dqDVpvofywcWVKxrf4%2Bf2pUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=c129cc71\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%BF%B4%E8%81%B2%E5%AE%A4%E6%95%88%E6%87%89</a>"},{"pid":"28f1c83d956a499d7b0054b